{"tid":1813504,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(民主手足) 倪晨曦 參演葉念琛賀歲片","createTime":"2020-01-06T10:20:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T04:10:42.000Z","uid":134071,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4772b50c49015e926abf93cc4cf7f2eae3aa96f9","tid":1813504,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T10:20:57.000Z","msg":"<strong>倪晨曦 在微博為「香港示威者」辯護</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1496064/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1496064/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n而家, 倪晨曦參演葉念琛賀歲片《我的筍盤男友》....<br />\n唔敢將套戲納入黃色經濟圈, 因為都明白一般港男睇葉念琛電影係活受罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;(雖然葉念琛都堅持拍本土戲, 唔鍾意佢既戲都respect佢)<br />\n<br />\n但起碼, 《我的筍盤男友》唔駛納入杯葛名單?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/72858\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfilmblog.com%2Farchives%2F72858&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDd%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=3b929ad2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/72858</a><br />\n<br />\n字眼方面，上方仍以「大年初一教你生擒千億首富」點題，下方則寫上「筍盤在手，長搵長有」。電影海報同時顯示除了陳家樂與李靖筠主演外，其他演員陣容包括林盛斌、郭奕芯、<strong>倪晨曦</strong>、糖妹、王卓淇、孫慧雪、張建聲、岑珈其與麥玲玲，而預告出現的吳家麗則作特別演出。觀乎演員陣容，未知大家對於葉念琛報導的第二部賀歲電影又有甚麼期望呢？"},{"pid":"0f639d9e189613c65e8e34e468e351f5ed20ceb6","tid":1813504,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T10:21:10.000Z","msg":"反而另一賀歲電影<strong>《肥龍過江 》</strong>要杯葛?<br />\n<br />\n肥龍過江 - CCTVB出品, 王晶編劇/監製/主演, 王祖藍, 陳友合演   (<strong>王晶, 王祖藍, 陳友都曾公開支持止暴制亂</strong>)"},{"pid":"371a8d8fb2eb5db31f08178827104aa1e3ab02ac","tid":1813504,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T10:25:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"425a49eeb3f9e697677c0103f8a5a7a23a104f6f","tid":1813504,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T10:25:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1395798c33f84f7cd